information: The company RVF RAIFFEISEN VIEH UND FLEISCH HESSEN E.G., is a Distributor, founded in 1968, which operates in the Cereals and grains industry. It also operates in the Shellfish and crustaceans, Fish, Cattle, and Pigs industries. It is based in Bad Hersfeld, Germany.
